---
import DocsLayout from "../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro";
import { FiList, FiInfo, FiZap, FiServer, FiAlertTriangle, FiAlertCircle, FiCheckCircle } from 'react-icons/fi';
---

<DocsLayout title="快速开始" description="快速上手咕哦！ ">
  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-800 mb-6 text-text">快速开始指南</h1>
    
    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted mb-8">
      按照以下步骤，快速加入咕哦！ ，开始你的音乐游戏之旅。
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-10">
      <!-- 版本选择组件 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-[#e2e8f0] shadow-sm">
        <h2 class="m-0 mb-4 text-xl font-700 flex items-center gap-2 text-[#0f172a]">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-md bg-primary/10 text-primary"><FiZap size={18} /></span>
          选择你的客户端版本
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted m-0 mb-5 text-[15px]">咕哦！ 同时兼容 osu!lazer 与 osu!stable。你可以任选其一开始，也可以双客户端并行。</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-6" id="version-tabs">
          <button data-target="ver-lazer" class="version-tab active inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-[14px] font-600 bg-primary text-white shadow-sm hover:opacity-95 transition">
            <FiZap size={16}/> lazer
          </button>
          <button data-target="ver-stable" class="version-tab inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-[14px] font-600 bg-[#6366f1]/15 text-[#4f46e5] hover:bg-[#6366f1]/25 transition">
            <FiServer size={16}/> stable
          </button>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <!-- lazer 面板 -->
          <div id="ver-lazer" class="version-panel block">
            <ol class="m-0 space-y-3 text-muted text-[15px]">
              <li>下载最新 osu!lazer 并完成首次启动。</li>
              <li>确保网络正常，使用默认登录面板登录账号。</li>
              <li>成绩提交与数据刷新可能有短暂延迟，稍等再刷新统计。</li>
              <li>更多细节参阅 <a href="/docs/lazer" class="text-primary no-underline hover:underline">lazer 教程</a>。</li>
            </ol>
            <div class="mt-4 p-4 rounded-lg border border-primary/30 bg-primary/10 text-[13px] text-[#0f172a] flex items-start gap-3">
              <FiCheckCircle class="mt-[2px] text-primary" size={16} />
              <span>lazer 与 stable 可共存，不会覆盖原有安装。</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- stable 面板 -->
          <div id="ver-stable" class="version-panel hidden">
            <ol class="m-0 space-y-3 text-muted text-[15px]">
              <li>安装或更新至最新 osu!stable。</li>
              <li>使用切换器或 hosts 方式完成连接。</li>
              <li>首次登录使用本站账号，确认排行榜是否可正常加载。</li>
              <li>更多细节参阅 <a href="/docs/stable" class="text-primary no-underline hover:underline">stable 教程</a>。</li>
            </ol>
            <div class="mt-4 p-4 rounded-lg border border-[#6366f1]/40 bg-[#6366f1]/10 text-[13px] text-[#0f172a] flex items-start gap-3">
              <FiAlertCircle class="mt-[2px] text-[#4f46e5]" size={16} />
              <span>修改 hosts 前请备份，错误条目可能导致其它网络问题。</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-[#f8fafc] p-6 rounded-xl border border-[#e2e8f0]">
        <h2 class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xl font-700 mb-4 text-text">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-md bg-primary/10 text-primary"><FiList size={18} /></span>
          步骤概览
        </h2>
        <ol class="space-y-3 text-muted">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-700">1</span>
            <span>访问首页，点击「查看文档」了解详细信息</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-700">2</span>
            <span>验证邮箱并完成账户注册</span>
          </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-700">3</span>
            <span>在个人中心下载支持本服的 osu! 客户端或配置切换器</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-700">4</span>
            <span>启动游戏并登录，开始游玩！</span>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>


      <div class="bg-accent/10 p-6 rounded-xl border border-accent/30">
        <h2 class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xl font-700 mb-4 text-accent">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-md bg-accent/30 text-[#173f40]"><FiInfo size={18} /></span>
          小贴士
        </h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-muted">
          <li>首次使用建议先阅读完整文档</li>
          <li>遇到问题可以查看常见问题解答</li>
          <li>加入社区可以获得最新更新信息</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- 告警块示例 -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-amber-300 bg-amber-50 p-4 text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-[#8a5200] flex gap-3">
          <FiAlertTriangle size={18} className="flex-shrink-0 mt-[2px]" />
          <div>
            <strong class="block mb-1">警告</strong>
            切换前请关闭正在运行的客户端，避免配置文件被占用或写入失败。
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-emerald-300 bg-emerald-50 p-4 text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-[#065f46] flex gap-3">
          <FiCheckCircle size={18} className="flex-shrink-0 mt-[2px]" />
          <div>
            <strong class="block mb-1">提示</strong>
            可同时保留两个客户端，互不影响，随时切换使用。
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 关于我们 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-[#e2e8f0] shadow-sm">
        <h2 class="m-0 mb-4 text-xl font-700 flex items-center gap-2 text-[#0f172a]">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-md bg-[#6366f1]/15 text-[#4f46e5]"><FiServer size={18} /></span>
          关于我们
        </h2>
  <p class="m-0 mb-3 text-muted leading-relaxed text-[15px]">我们提供兼容 lazer / stable 的多模式服务器，支持 RX / AP、改名与 PP 刷新，并欢迎社区协作。</p>
        <ul class="m-0 text-[14px] text-[#475569] space-y-1">
          <li>持续迭代：跟进上游公式与客户端改动。</li>
          <li>数据透明：开放说明计算逻辑与版本更新。</li>
          <li>社区协作：欢迎反馈与贡献文档 / 工具。</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 bg-white border border-[#e2e8f0] rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h2 class="m-0 mb-4 text-[18px] font-700 flex items-center gap-2 text-[#0f172a]">
          下一步：选择你的客户端
        </h2>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a href="/docs/lazer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg no-underline bg-primary text-white text-[14px] font-600 hover:opacity-90 transition">
            <FiZap size={16} /> 查看 lazer 教程
          </a>
          <a href="/docs/stable" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg no-underline bg-[#6366f1]/20 text-[#4f46e5] text-[14px] font-600 hover:bg-[#6366f1]/30 transition">
            <FiServer size={16} /> 查看 stable 教程
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</DocsLayout>

<script>
  const tabButtons = document.querySelectorAll('.version-tab');
  const panels = document.querySelectorAll('.version-panel');
  tabButtons.forEach(btn => {
    btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const target = btn.getAttribute('data-target');
      tabButtons.forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active','bg-primary','text-white','shadow-sm'));
      tabButtons.forEach(b => b.classList.add('bg-[#6366f1]/15','text-[#4f46e5]'));
      btn.classList.add('active','bg-primary','text-white','shadow-sm');
      btn.classList.remove('bg-[#6366f1]/15','text-[#4f46e5]');
      panels.forEach(p => p.classList.add('hidden'));
      const panel = document.getElementById(target || '');
      panel?.classList.remove('hidden');
      panel?.classList.add('block');
    });
  });
</script>

<div slot="after" />


